		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Pretty much.<br /><br />I think I have an easy way around the collision box problem.  For the player-enemy collision, I cheated a bit and used point-box collision, to make collision more forgiving.  I could just have a collision point variable, so I can just move the collision point.

		

		</td>
